# ::snt-1 A group of boys in a yard is playing and a man is standing in the background
(z1 / and
      :op1 (z2 / play-01
            :ARG0 (z3 / group
                  :consist-of (z4 / boy))
            :location (z5 / yard))
      :op2 (z6 / stand-01
            :ARG1 (z7 / man)
            :ARG2 (z8 / background)))

# ::snt-2 A group of kids is playing in a yard and an old man is standing in the background
(z1 / and
      :op1 (z2 / play-01
            :ARG0 (z3 / group
                  :consist-of (z4 / kid))
            :location (z5 / yard))
      :op2 (z6 / stand-01
            :ARG1 (z7 / man
                  :mod (z8 / old))
            :ARG2 (z9 / background)))

# ::snt-3 The kids are playing outdoors near a man with a smile
(z1 / play-01
      :ARG0 (z2 / kid)
      :location (z3 / outdoors
            :ARG1-of (z4 / near-02
                  :ARG2 (z5 / man
                        :ARG0-of (z6 / smile-01)))))

# ::snt-4 There is no boy playing outdoors and there is no man smiling
(z1 / and
      :op1 (z2 / boy
            :polarity -
            :ARG0-of (z3 / play-01
                  :location (z4 / outdoors)))
      :op2 (z5 / man
            :polarity -
            :ARG0-of (z6 / smile-01)))

      :op1 (z2 / stand-01
            :ARG1 (z3 / man)
            :ARG2 (z4 / mountain
                  :mod (z5 / rocky)))
      :op2 (z6 / cloud
            :ARG1-of (z7 / gray-02)
            :location (z8 / background)))

(z1 / ride-01
      :ARG0 (z2 / woman)
      :ARG1 (z3 / scooter)
      :purpose (z4 / water))

            :location (z5 / air)))

# ::snt-9825 The cheerleaders are parading and wearing black, pink and white uniforms

            :ARG0 (z3 / cheerleader))
      :op2 (z4 / wear-01

                  :op1 (z6 / uniform
                        :ARG1-of (z7 / black-04))
                  :op2 (z8 / uniform
                        :ARG1-of (z9 / pink-04))
                  :op3 (z10 / uniform
                        :ARG1-of (z11 / white-03)))))

                  :ARG1-of (z6 / black-04)))
